---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Boing Network"
  description="Boing Network ‚Äî Authentic. Decentralized. Optimal. Quality-Assured. Authentic L1 blockchain built from first principles. Swap, stake, and build on the Boing ecosystem."
  canonical="/"
  pageClass="page-landing"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero" id="hero">
    <!-- Robot hero: extracted Boing robot (from hero image) with 3D motion over environment background -->
    <div class="hero-robot-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="hero-robot-3d">
        <img src="/assets/mascot-excited.png" alt="" class="hero-robot-img" width="480" height="480" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="hero-orb hero-orb-1"></div>
      <div class="hero-orb hero-orb-2"></div>
      <div class="hero-orb hero-orb-3"></div>
      <div class="float-particle float-particle-1"></div>
      <div class="float-particle float-particle-2"></div>
      <div class="float-particle float-particle-3"></div>
      <div class="float-particle float-particle-4"></div>
      <div class="float-particle float-particle-5"></div>
      <div class="shooting-star shooting-star-1"><div class="shooting-star-line line-1"></div></div>
      <div class="shooting-star shooting-star-2"><div class="shooting-star-line line-2"></div></div>
      <div class="shooting-star shooting-star-3"><div class="shooting-star-line line-3"></div></div>
      <div class="shooting-star shooting-star-4"><div class="shooting-star-line line-4"></div></div>
      <div class="shooting-star shooting-star-5"><div class="shooting-star-line line-5"></div></div>
      <div class="shooting-star shooting-star-6"><div class="shooting-star-line line-6"></div></div>
      <div class="shooting-star shooting-star-7"><div class="shooting-star-line line-7"></div></div>
      <div class="shooting-star shooting-star-8"><div class="shooting-star-line line-8"></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <picture class="hero-logo-picture">
        <source srcset="/assets/logo-dark-transparent.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)" />
        <source srcset="/assets/logo-light-transparent.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)" />
        <img src="/assets/logo-dark-transparent.png" alt="Boing Network" class="hero-logo-img" width="200" height="80" />
      </picture>
      <h1 class="hero-title gradient-text-hero animate-pulse-glow">Boing Network</h1>
      <p class="tagline gradient-text-hero">Authentic. Decentralized. Optimal. Quality-Assured.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <span class="hero-highlight"><span class="hl-icon">üîê</span> Security</span>
        <span class="hero-highlight"><span class="hl-icon">‚ö°</span> Scalability</span>
        <span class="hero-highlight"><span class="hl-icon">üåê</span> Decentralization</span>
        <span class="hero-highlight"><span class="hl-icon">‚úì</span> Authenticity</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cta">
        <a href="/network/testnet" class="btn btn-testnet">Join Testnet</a>
        <a href="/docs/getting-started" class="btn btn-secondary">Get Started</a>
        <a href="#tokenomics" class="btn btn-outline">Explore</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Pillars of the Boing Network -->
  <section class="section section-alt fade-in-up" id="pillars">
    <h2 class="display-title">The Pillars of the Boing Network</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">Six foundational principles that define who we are.</p>
    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <img src="/assets/pillar-security.png" alt="Security" class="pillar-img" width="200" height="280" />
        <h3>Security</h3>
        <p>Safety and correctness first ‚Äî always over speed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <img src="/assets/pillar-scalability.png" alt="Scalability" class="pillar-img" width="200" height="280" />
        <h3>Scalability</h3>
        <p>High throughput without compromising the other pillars.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <img src="/assets/pillar-decentralization.png" alt="Decentralization" class="pillar-img" width="200" height="280" />
        <h3>Decentralization</h3>
        <p>Anyone can participate. No one can shut the door.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <img src="/assets/pillar-authenticity.png" alt="Authenticity" class="pillar-img" width="200" height="280" />
        <h3>Authenticity</h3>
        <p>One chain, one identity ‚Äî authentic and independent.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <img src="/assets/pillar-transparency.png" alt="Transparency" class="pillar-img" width="200" height="280" />
        <h3>Transparency</h3>
        <p>100% open ‚Äî in design, governance, and operations. Trust through verification.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <img src="/assets/pillar-quality.png" alt="Quality Assurance" class="pillar-img" width="200" height="280" />
        <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
        <p>Legitimate purpose only ‚Äî enforced by the network.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tokenomics -->
  <section class="section section-alt fade-in-up" id="tokenomics">
    <h2>Tokenomics</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">Sustainable value design ‚Äî <strong>uncapped total supply</strong> with a <strong>set initial supply</strong> at mainnet launch. When circulating supply reaches the floor, new waves are minted to rebalance.</p>
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-card fade-in-up delay-1"><span class="stat-value">Uncapped</span><span class="stat-label">Total Supply</span></div>
      <div class="stat-card fade-in-up delay-2"><span class="stat-value">Set at launch</span><span class="stat-label">Initial Supply</span></div>
      <div class="stat-card fade-in-up delay-3"><span class="stat-value">~2s</span><span class="stat-label">Block Time</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-card chart-fullwidth">
      <h3>Initial Supply Allocation</h3>
      <p class="chart-intro">How the fixed initial supply (at mainnet launch) is allocated. Staking rewards are topped up by new waves when supply reaches the floor, so the initial allocation leans more toward treasury and community.</p>
      <div class="chart-wrapper chart-supply chart-pie-wrap">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="supply-pie-svg">
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="none" class="stroke-teal" stroke-width="40" stroke-dasharray="138.2 113.1" stroke-dashoffset="0" transform="rotate(-90 50 50)" stroke-linecap="butt" />
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="none" class="stroke-cyan" stroke-width="40" stroke-dasharray="75.4 175.9" stroke-dashoffset="-138.2" transform="rotate(-90 50 50)" stroke-linecap="butt" />
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="none" class="stroke-success" stroke-width="40" stroke-dasharray="37.7 213.6" stroke-dashoffset="-213.6" transform="rotate(-90 50 50)" stroke-linecap="butt" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <ul class="legend legend-inline">
        <li><span class="dot dot-teal"></span> Staking Rewards 55%</li>
        <li><span class="dot dot-cyan"></span> Treasury 30%</li>
        <li><span class="dot dot-success"></span> Community & Grants 15%</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="chart-note">Total supply is uncapped. Initial supply is fixed at mainnet launch; new waves mint when circulating supply reaches the floor.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="charts-row">
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>Fee Allocation</h3>
        <div class="chart-wrapper chart-doughnut">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="doughnut-svg">
            <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="none" class="stroke-teal" stroke-width="20" stroke-dasharray="201 50.3" stroke-dashoffset="0" transform="rotate(-90 50 50)" />
            <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="none" class="stroke-cyan" stroke-width="20" stroke-dasharray="50.3 201" stroke-dashoffset="-201" transform="rotate(-90 50 50)" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <ul class="legend">
          <li><span class="dot dot-teal"></span> Validators 80%</li>
          <li><span class="dot dot-cyan"></span> Treasury 20%</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>Emission Schedule</h3>
        <div class="chart-wrapper chart-line">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 120" class="line-svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="emissionGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="var(--accent-teal)" stop-opacity="0.3" />
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="var(--accent-teal)" stop-opacity="0" />
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
            <polyline points="0,24 33,48 67,66 100,79 133,90 200,108 200,120 0,120" fill="url(#emissionGrad)" stroke="none" />
            <polyline points="0,24 33,48 67,66 100,79 133,90 200,108" fill="none" class="stroke-teal" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="value-loop"><strong>Usage ‚Üë</strong> ‚Üí Fees ‚Üë ‚Üí Validators & Treasury ‚Üë ‚Üí Security & Ecosystem ‚Üë ‚Üí <strong>Value ‚Üë</strong></p>
  </section>

  <!-- Roadmap -->
  <section class="section fade-in-up" id="roadmap">
    <h2>Roadmap</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">Phased build from first principles.</p>
    <div class="timeline-compact">
      <div class="t-item complete"><span class="t-marker">‚úì</span><span>Foundation</span></div>
      <div class="t-item complete"><span class="t-marker">‚úì</span><span>Networking</span></div>
      <div class="t-item complete"><span class="t-marker">‚úì</span><span>Verkle & VM</span></div>
      <div class="t-item in-progress"><span class="t-marker">‚óè</span><span>PoS & Production</span></div>
      <div class="t-item in-progress"><span class="t-marker">‚óè</span><span>UX & Automation</span></div>
      <div class="t-item planned"><span class="t-marker">‚óã</span><span>Cross-chain</span></div>
      <div class="t-item planned"><span class="t-marker">‚óã</span><span>Testnet & Mainnet</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ecosystem -->
  <section class="section section-alt fade-in-up" id="ecosystem">
    <h2>Ecosystem</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">Applications building on Boing Network.</p>
    <div class="apps-row">
      <a href="https://boing.finance" class="app-card featured" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <h3>boing.finance</h3>
        <p>Swap, bridge, deploy tokens, manage liquidity across EVM & Solana.</p>
        <span class="app-status live">Live</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/docs/getting-started" class="app-card">
        <h3>Boing Network</h3>
        <p>Run a node, stake, participate in governance. The foundation layer.</p>
        <span class="app-status live">Live</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/developers/quickstart" class="app-card">
        <h3>Build on Boing</h3>
        <p>Native AA, adaptive gas, success-based incentives for developers.</p>
        <span class="app-status build">Build</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Innovations -->
  <section class="section fade-in-up" id="innovations">
    <h2>Unique Innovations</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h3>Native Account Abstraction</h3><p>Gasless txs, social recovery, session keys ‚Äî built into the protocol.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Adaptive Gas Model</h3><p>Dynamic gas that responds to network conditions with predictable caps.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Cross-Chain DeFi Hub</h3><p>Protocol-level primitives for liquidity routing across chains.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Transparent Slashing</h3><p>Auditable slashing conditions and appeal mechanisms.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testnet CTA (incentivize participation) -->
  <section class="section fade-in-up" id="testnet-cta">
    <div class="testnet-banner">
      <h3>üåê Join the Testnet</h3>
      <p>Run a node, get testnet BOING from the faucet, and help secure the network. Single node for local dev or multi-node to join the public testnet.</p>
      <div class="testnet-banner-btns">
        <a href="/network/testnet" class="btn btn-testnet">Join Testnet</a>
        <a href="/network/faucet" class="btn btn-secondary">Get testnet BOING</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <section class="section fade-in-up">
    <div class="cta-banner">
      <h3>üöÄ Build on Boing Network</h3>
      <p>Authentic L1 blockchain built from first principles. Native AA, adaptive gas, cross-chain DeFi hub.</p>
      <div class="cta-banner-links">
        <a href="/network/testnet">Join Testnet</a>
        <span class="sep">‚Ä¢</span>
        <a href="/docs/getting-started">Get Started</a>
        <span class="sep">‚Ä¢</span>
        <a href="/developers/quickstart">Developers</a>
        <span class="sep">‚Ä¢</span>
        <a href="https://boing.finance" target="_blank" rel="noopener">boing.finance</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Resources -->
  <section class="section section-alt links-section fade-in-up">
    <h2>Resources</h2>
    <div class="link-grid">
      <a href="/network/testnet" class="link-highlight link-3d">Join Testnet</a>
      <a href="/network/faucet" class="link-highlight link-3d">Faucet</a>
      <a href="/docs/getting-started" class="link-3d">Getting Started</a>
      <a href="/docs/rpc-api" class="link-3d">RPC API</a>
      <a href="/developers/quickstart" class="link-3d">Developer Quickstart</a>
      <a href="/network/status" class="link-3d">Network Status</a>
      <a href="/about" class="link-3d">About</a>
      <a href="/community" class="link-3d">Community</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Section-by-section scroll snap (homepage only) */
  :global(html.page-home) { scroll-snap-type: y mandatory; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  :global(html.page-home) .hero,
  :global(html.page-home) .section { scroll-snap-align: start; scroll-snap-stop: always; min-height: 100vh; }

  /* Hero + animation */
  .hero { position: relative; text-align: center; padding: 5rem 2rem; overflow: hidden; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; grid-template-rows: auto auto; align-items: center; justify-items: center; min-height: 85vh; gap: 1rem; }
  .hero-content { order: 1; }
  .hero-robot-wrap { order: 2; }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; grid-template-rows: 1fr; gap: 2rem; text-align: left; }
    .hero-content { order: unset; margin: 0; max-width: 520px; justify-self: end; }
    .hero-robot-wrap { order: unset; }
    .hero-highlights { justify-content: flex-start; }
    .cta { justify-content: flex-start; }
  }
  .hero-robot-wrap {
    position: relative;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 2;
    perspective: 1400px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .hero-robot-wrap { position: absolute; right: 0; bottom: 0; top: 0; left: 45%; }
  }
  .hero-robot-3d {
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    animation: hero-robot-float 7s ease-in-out infinite;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(0, 229, 204, 0.2)) drop-shadow(0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3));
  }
  .hero-robot-wrap .hero-robot-3d {
    position: relative;
    width: min(55vw, 420px);
    height: min(55vw, 420px);
    max-width: 480px;
    max-height: 75vh;
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .hero-robot-wrap .hero-robot-3d { width: min(42vw, 480px); height: min(42vw, 480px); }
  }
  .hero-robot-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    object-position: center bottom;
    animation: hero-robot-glow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes hero-robot-float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotateY(-6deg) rotateX(3deg); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-14px) rotateY(4deg) rotateX(-2deg); }
  }
  @keyframes hero-robot-glow {
    0%, 100% { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(0, 229, 204, 0.2)); opacity: 1; }
    50% { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 56px rgba(0, 229, 204, 0.35)); opacity: 0.98; }
  }
  .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
  .hero-orb { position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(80px); opacity: 0.4; animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .hero-orb-1 { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-teal) 0%, transparent 70%); top: -20%; left: 10%; animation-delay: 0s; }
  .hero-orb-2 { width: 300px; height: 300px; background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-cyan) 0%, transparent 70%); bottom: -10%; right: 15%; animation-delay: -7s; }
  .hero-orb-3 { width: 250px; height: 250px; background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-teal) 0%, transparent 70%); top: 30%; right: 5%; animation-delay: -14s; }
  @keyframes float { 0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); } 33% { transform: translate(30px, -20px) scale(1.05); } 66% { transform: translate(-20px, 15px) scale(0.95); } }
  /* Shooting stars ‚Äî gradient lines inspired by boing.finance */
  .shooting-star { position: absolute; width: 0; height: 0; overflow: visible; }
  .shooting-star-line {
    position: absolute; width: 128px; height: 2px; left: 0; top: 0;
    border-radius: 1px;
    transform-origin: left center;
  }
  /* Each line rotation matches keyframe movement. Angles: 0¬∞=right, 90¬∞=down, 180¬∞=left. vw units preserve angle. */
  .line-1 { background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--glow-cyan), var(--accent-teal)); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--glow-cyan); transform: rotate(-16deg); }
  .line-2 { background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, var(--glow-blue), var(--accent-cyan)); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--glow-blue); transform-origin: right center; transform: rotate(-55deg); }
  .line-3 { background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--glow-cyan), var(--accent-cyan)); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--glow-cyan); transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .line-4 { background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, var(--glow-cyan), var(--accent-teal)); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--glow-cyan-subtle); transform-origin: right center; transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .line-5 { background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--glow-cyan), var(--accent-teal)); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--glow-cyan-subtle); transform: rotate(-10deg); }
  .line-6 { background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, var(--glow-blue), var(--accent-cyan)); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--glow-blue); transform-origin: right center; transform: rotate(-17deg); }
  .line-7 { background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--glow-cyan), var(--accent-cyan)); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--glow-cyan-subtle); transform: rotate(35deg); }
  .line-8 { background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, var(--glow-cyan), var(--accent-teal)); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--glow-cyan-subtle); transform-origin: right center; transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .shooting-star-1 { top: 25%; left: 0; animation: shoot1 8s linear infinite; opacity: 0.6; }
  .shooting-star-2 { top: 33%; right: 0; animation: shoot2 12s linear infinite; animation-delay: -2s; opacity: 0.5; }
  .shooting-star-3 { bottom: 25%; left: 25%; animation: shoot3 10s linear infinite; animation-delay: -4s; opacity: 0.4; }
  .shooting-star-4 { top: 50%; right: 33%; animation: shoot4 15s linear infinite; animation-delay: -7s; opacity: 0.3; }
  .shooting-star-5 { top: 17%; right: 25%; animation: shoot5 6s linear infinite; animation-delay: -1s; opacity: 0.5; }
  .shooting-star-6 { bottom: 33%; left: 33%; animation: shoot6 9s linear infinite; animation-delay: -5s; opacity: 0.45; }
  .shooting-star-7 { top: 40%; left: 17%; animation: shoot7 11s linear infinite; animation-delay: -6s; opacity: 0.4; }
  .shooting-star-8 { top: 75%; right: 17%; animation: shoot8 14s linear infinite; animation-delay: -9s; opacity: 0.35; }
  .float-particle { position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent-teal), var(--accent-cyan)); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--glow-cyan); animation: floatSlow 6s ease-in-out infinite, pulseFade 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .float-particle-1 { width: 4px; height: 4px; top: 15%; left: 20%; animation-delay: 0s, 0s; }
  .float-particle-2 { width: 2px; height: 2px; top: 65%; right: 25%; animation-delay: -2s, -0.5s; }
  .float-particle-3 { width: 2px; height: 2px; bottom: 30%; left: 50%; animation-delay: -4s, -1s; }
  .float-particle-4 { width: 3px; height: 3px; top: 40%; left: 25%; background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent-cyan), var(--accent-teal)); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--glow-blue); animation-delay: -1s, -0.3s; }
  .float-particle-5 { width: 2px; height: 2px; top: 75%; right: 15%; animation-delay: -3s, -0.8s; }
  /* Movement (dx,dy) uses vw so angle stays consistent. dx:dy ratio = tan(angle). */
  @keyframes shoot1 { 0% { transform: translate(0, 0); opacity: 0; } 10% { opacity: 0.6; } 90% { opacity: 0.6; } 100% { transform: translate(100vw, -28vw); opacity: 0; } } /* -16¬∞ */
  @keyframes shoot2 { 0% { transform: translate(0, 0); opacity: 0; } 10% { opacity: 0.5; } 90% { opacity: 0.5; } 100% { transform: translate(-100vw, 143vw); opacity: 0; } } /* 125¬∞ dy/dx=tan(125¬∞)=1.43 */
  @keyframes shoot3 { 0% { transform: translate(0, 0); opacity: 0; } 10% { opacity: 0.4; } 90% { opacity: 0.4; } 100% { transform: translate(100vw, 100vw); opacity: 0; } } /* 45¬∞ */
  @keyframes shoot4 { 0% { transform: translate(0, 0); opacity: 0; } 10% { opacity: 0.3; } 90% { opacity: 0.3; } 100% { transform: translate(-80vw, -80vw); opacity: 0; } } /* 225¬∞ */
  @keyframes shoot5 { 0% { transform: translate(0, 0); opacity: 0; } 5% { opacity: 0.5; } 95% { opacity: 0.5; } 100% { transform: translate(100vw, -18vw); opacity: 0; } } /* -10¬∞ */
  @keyframes shoot6 { 0% { transform: translate(0, 0); opacity: 0; } 8% { opacity: 0.45; } 92% { opacity: 0.45; } 100% { transform: translate(-90vw, 27vw); opacity: 0; } } /* 163¬∞ tan‚âà0.3 */
  @keyframes shoot7 { 0% { transform: translate(0, 0); opacity: 0; } 12% { opacity: 0.4; } 88% { opacity: 0.4; } 100% { transform: translate(100vw, 70vw); opacity: 0; } } /* 35¬∞ */
  @keyframes shoot8 { 0% { transform: translate(0, 0); opacity: 0; } 7% { opacity: 0.35; } 93% { opacity: 0.35; } 100% { transform: translate(-60vw, -60vw); opacity: 0; } } /* 225¬∞ */
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 3; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
